  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Promote and sell <strong>Prepaid / Stored Value Cards</strong> to customers</p></li><li><p>Explain the benefits and usage of prepaid balances across our venue</p></li><li><p>Understand customer needs and recommend suitable prepaid packages</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong customer relationships</p></li><li><p>Achieve individual and team sales targets</p></li><li><p>Assist customers with payment, activation, and usage enquiries</p></li><li><p>Support in-store promotions and sales activities</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 18 years old, presentable, with good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Sales experience is an advantage (service, hospitality, lifestyle, wellness industries preferred)</p></li><li><p>Strong customer-oriented mindset and sales motivation</p></li><li><p>Able to work shifts, including weekends and public holidays</p></li><li><p><strong>Fluent in both Chinese and English is an advantage</strong></p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Competitive basic salary with <strong>attractive commission structure</strong>Clear career progression opportunities</p></li><li><p>Product and sales training provided</p></li><li><p>Stable customer base and premium working environment</p></li><li><p>Staff benefits and internal privileges</p></li></ul>",
